		<h3 title='Your Changing Needs'><a href='#'></a></h3>
		<div class='panelContent nonFeedback'>
			<p>
				In today's financial environment it is difficult to obtain financing no matter what your credit history.
				The <span class='Highlight'>ONLY</span> way that makes sense during these tough financial times is to
				use cash-backed bank instruments like a Standby Letter of Credit (SBLC), Bank Guarantee (BG), or
				Certificates of Deposit (CDs) as collateral.
			</p>
			<p>
				We also can <span class='Highlight'>optionally</span> monetize or provide <a href='./BankInstrumentFinancing.php'>loans</a> against
